1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,600
What if your body is a master of balance?

2
00:00:03,600 --> 00:00:09,200
Homeostasis is how your body keeps everything in check—temperature, blood sugar, even pH levels.

3
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:11,600
When you’re too hot, you sweat.

4
00:00:11,600 --> 00:00:15,200
When you’re low on sugar, your body craves food.

5
00:00:15,200 --> 00:00:16,800
It’s a constant dance.

6
00:00:16,800 --> 00:00:23,200
Studies show that disruptions in homeostasis can lead to serious health issues like diabetes or hypothermia.

7
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:30,400
So the next time you feel off, remember, your body is fighting to bring you back to balance.

8
00:00:30,400 --> 00:00:33,200
Curious about other wonders of your body?

9
00:00:33,200 --> 00:00:34,800
Hit subscribe for more!
